<% content_for(:title, "Zero Waste Week — Christopher Quentin") %>

<section class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 pt-20 pb-16">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
    <span class="inline-block w-[34px] h-px bg-accent"></span>
    <span class="font-mono text-[12px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-accent">Zero Waste Week · July</span>
  </div>
  <h1 class="font-serif font-medium tracking-[-0.02em] text-ink mt-6 mb-0"
      style="font-size: clamp(40px, 5.5vw, 72px); line-height: 1.0;">
    Zero Waste Week.
  </h1>
  <p class="text-[16px] text-muted mt-5 max-w-[640px]">
    Thirty-two friends and family pledging to live without waste — one week in Christopher&rsquo;s honor.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 pb-20">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.5fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-14">
    <%# Left column — prose %>
    <div>
      <div class="font-serif text-[19px] leading-relaxed text-ink space-y-6">
        <p>
          Christopher&rsquo;s Zero Waste Week &mdash; In July we celebrated Chris&rsquo; commitment to zero
          waste by organizing a zero waste week! A group of 32 of his friends and family pledged to go
          zero waste for a week and share their experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%# Right column — image grid %>
    <aside class="self-start">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <img src="https://christopherquentin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Screen-Shot-2021-09-13-at-10.56.14-AM.png"
             alt="Zero Waste Week"
             class="rounded-[3px] border border-ink/8 w-full aspect-square object-cover col-span-2">
        <img src="https://christopherquentin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/8C42D473-806C-4DF1-98AC-77E12519C1C1_4_5005_c.jpeg"
             alt="Zero Waste Week"
             class="rounded-[3px] border border-ink/8 w-full aspect-square object-cover">
        <img src="https://christopherquentin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/72E1FB61-79A8-435F-986A-1756F4ED4366.jpeg"
             alt="Zero Waste Week"
             class="rounded-[3px] border border-ink/8 w-full aspect-square object-cover">
        <img src="https://christopherquentin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/7E417DF9-E682-4B6A-AC97-7CAEEEB29F36.jpeg"
             alt="Zero Waste Week"
             class="rounded-[3px] border border-ink/8 w-full aspect-square object-cover col-span-2">
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
